videos.headline: Trick play leads to Kentucky field goal
videos.description: On an end around, Garrett Johnson's 11-yard run leads to a Kentucky field goal.

videos.headline: Boyle's TD pass to Markush puts Eastern Kentucky on top
videos.description: Tim Boyle's seven-yard touchdown pass to Ryan Markush gives Eastern Kentucky a 7-3 lead.

videos.headline: Scott goes untouched into the end zone
videos.description: LJ Scott's seven-yard touchdown run extend's Eastern Kentucky's lead.

videos.headline: Conrad finds Johnson in stride for Kentucky TD
videos.description: C.J. Conrad completes a 23-yard touchdown pass to Stephen Johnson in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Stoops: Kentucky needs to be more consistent
videos.description: Kentucky head coach Mark Stoops says his team has to make better plays on the ball in the second half.

videos.headline: Snell breaks tackles, scores TD for Kentucky
videos.description: Benny Snell's 25-yard touchdown run gives Kentucky the lead.

videos.headline: Johnson escapes tackles, scores TD
videos.description: Stephen Johnson's 21-yard touchdown run extends Kentucky's lead in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Kentucky's Edwards picks off EKU's Boyle
videos.description: Mike Edwards intercepts Tim Boyle late in the fourth quarter to end Eastern Kentucky's drive.

videos.headline: Johnson on win over Eastern Kentucky
videos.description: Kentucky quarterback Stephen Johnson breaks down the Wildcats' 27-16 comeback win.

videos.headline: Stoops: Game won in 4th quarter
videos.description: Mark Stoops is pleased with Kentucky's win, but says his team still has a lot to improve on.

videos.headline: Ware breaks down Kentucky's win
videos.description: Andre Ware discusses what Kentucky did in the second half to propel them to a 27-16 win over Eastern Kentucky.
